headline: Costco Wholesale Corporation Reports December Sales Results
summary: ISSAQUAH, Wash., Jan. 08, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Costco Wholesale Corporation (“Costco” or the “Company”) (Nasdaq: COST) today reported net sales of $27.52 billion for the retail month of December, the five weeks ended January 5, 2025, an increase of 9.9 percent from $25.03 billion last year. Net sales for the first eighteen weeks were $94.04 billion, an increase of 8.0 percent from $87.07 billion last year.
